这是Fontaines DC的亲密“浪漫”伦敦表演的情况https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-dc-london-camden-electric-ballroom-setlist-footage-photos-3786117?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=fontaines-dc-london-camden-electric-宴会厅定居者 - 史图斯Anagricel DuranFri, 23 Aug 2024 06:27:19 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3786117 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Fontaines DC在罗马的舞台上表演。 （Valeria Magri/sopa图像/lightrocket通过盖蒂图片照片）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>庆祝乐队第四张专辑发行的 Camden Electric Ballroom 演出吸引了 Harry Styles、Cillian Murphy 和 Florence Welch 等人的参与</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-london-camden-electric-ballroom-setlist-footage-photos-3786117">这是Fontaines DC亲密的“浪漫”伦敦节目</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上的帖子。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Fontaines DC在罗马的舞台上表演。 （Valeria Magri/sopa图像/lightrocket通过盖蒂图片照片）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a>昨晚（8月22日）在伦敦举行了一次亲密的惊喜演出，以发行他们的新专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/fontaines-d-c-romance-review-3784445">Romance</a> ”  - 查看镜头，Setlist等。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/fontaines-d-c-grian-chatten-interview-at-home-romance-favourite-new-album-3784142">与Fontaines DC的Grian Chatten在家：“我们的个性比我们发出的声音更大”</a></strong></li></ul><p>都柏林乐队 - 由<a href="/artists/Grian-Chatten">Grian Chatten</a> ，Tom Coll，Conor Curley，Conor Deegan III和Carlos O&#39;Connell组成， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-announce-intimate-surprise-london-romance-album-release-show-3785009">接管了伦敦的标志性电动宴会厅</a>，以庆祝发行第四张专辑的发行。</p><p>他们在卡姆登（Camden）的场地上玩了1500名售罄的人群，那里的人看到了<a href="/artist/Harry-Styles">哈利·斯泰尔斯（Harry Styles）</a> ，<a href="/artists/Cillian-Murphy">西利安·墨菲（Cillian Murphy）</a> ，<a href="/artists/Florence-Welch">佛罗伦萨·韦尔奇（Florence Welch）</a>等人。</p><p>为了开始夜晚，Coll，Deegan和Carlos登上了舞台，因为Lime Green Lights在Curly（将他的6弦换成低音吉他）时闪烁，开始了&#39;Romance&#39;&#39;Romance的令人困扰和令人困扰的冠军头衔的开场笔记。</p><p>查滕（Chatten）在舞台上行走，穿着黑色T恤，黑色苏格兰短裙，白色膝盖高的袜子，黑色战斗靴和一双深色太阳镜，这已成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-explain-neon-and-ridiculous-sound-of-romance-and-bands-new-look-3784877">乐队当前时代的制服</a>。一个巨大的巴勒斯坦国旗装饰了乐队的键盘设置， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-new-songs-live-romance-favourite-brooklyn-warsaw-video-photos-3754714">在与以色列的持续战争中表明了他们对国家的持续支持</a>。</p><p>从那里开始，Fontaines DC跳入了旧的最爱“ Jackie Down the Line”，“电视转播的思想”，“ Roman Holiday”和“ Big Shot”和“ Big Shot”，然后对人群进行了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-fontaines-d-c-debut-woozy-and-aggressive-new-song-death-kink-3782900">现场表演“ Death Kink”的现场表演</a>，这是倒数第二个浪漫的曲目。 &#39;。</p><p>乐队演奏了横跨他们的四张专辑的曲目，包括最近发行的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-fontaines-d-c-s-existential-new-single-in-the-modern-world-3785348">现代世界</a>”，“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-dc-debut-heres-the-thing-new-song-in-the-modern-world-3784474">这是事物</a>”和“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-release-wistful-new-single-favourite-3766794#:~:text=Now%2C%20Fontaines%20D.C.%20have%20dropped,%2C%20two%20worlds%20spinning%20forever%E2%80%9D.">最爱</a>”。为了结束当晚，查顿和他的合作伙伴带来了一场震撼人心的表演《我爱你》——在表演中，可以看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392"><em>奥本海默</em></a>演员墨菲手里拿着一品脱吉尼斯黑啤酒用头撞着歌——然后以《浪漫的主打单曲》结束。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/fontaines-d-c-starbust-track-review-xl-romance-3618968">星空</a>&#39;。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-_fQvhoW9q/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox